{"tid":710901,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"連千秋王子都要食高鈞賢二手西","createTime":"2018-06-21T06:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T12:40:32.000Z","uid":66260,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f27c3ecd7f1a3268a2c915c82c2f200bf4a90797","tid":710901,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:29:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180621/58344509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180621%2F58344509&d=ghkbBml4OP7faEnvecWIPgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=4ec10828\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180621%2F58344509&h=7e534daa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180621/58344509</a><br />\n<br />\n38歲日本男星玉木宏結束王老五生涯，今日香港時間凌晨宣佈閃婚消息，新娘子係32歲演技派女星木南晴夏，兩人已擇日在下星期二即本月26日結婚成為夫妻，消息震驚藝能界。<br />\n<br />\n木南晴夏憑電影《20世紀少年》嶄露頭角，近年演出大量日劇及電影，目前參演TBS台熱播劇《花過天晴》，年前夥玉木宏合演特備劇《女人的勳章》時秘密撻着，而木南晴夏多年來亦不少圈中男友，佢曾與香港先生高鈞賢發展異地戀，之後又跟樂隊ONE OK ROCK結他手Ryota玩姐弟戀，近日驚爆秘戀「千秋王子」玉木宏，兩人原來早在8年前已在朋友介紹下認識，當拍攝《女人的勳章》才結為情侶關係。<br />\n玉木宏靠《交響情人夢》走紅亞洲，當「野田妹」上野樹里於兩年前嫁人，今日輪到「千秋王子」傳來喜訊，而玉木宏多年來先後跟女星加藤羅莎、島谷瞳、北川景子傳出緋聞。"},{"pid":"969b4a4a8f984d1b9e057505e8e7a43479057fe4","tid":710901,"uid":66260,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:30:10.000Z","msg":"btw阿紫終於做左人妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/143008_8607a4ef9b05ddb5199c9f401c61fe41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F143008_8607a4ef9b05ddb5199c9f401c61fe41.jpg&h=fc813cfa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c339efe45ba5cf11b095206280c03a06e0e40421","tid":710901,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T06:40:03.000Z","msg":