rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4556d611e85854fd8568af07a7b15ce6fbf8773f","tid":710901,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇唔出高鈞賢都識幾多人，之前見佢上支版看得見的聲音，佢同胡歌都係朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681a01b38e4b24c729c18d7ed1239093e521e61f","tid":710901,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4556d611e85854fd8568af07a7b15ce6fbf8773f","tid":710901,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇唔出高鈞賢都識幾多人，之前見佢上支版看得見的聲音，佢同胡歌都係朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T11:34:09.000Z","msg":"真唔真呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba02e6224ce5e83551de6c8da1bb942c30917bf7","tid":710901,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"681a01b38e4b24c729c18d7ed1239093e521e61f","tid":710901,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4556d611e85854fd8568af07a7b15ce6fbf8773f","tid":710901,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇唔出高鈞賢都識幾多人，之前見佢上支版看得見的聲音，佢同胡歌都係朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T11:34:09.000Z","msg":"真唔真呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T11:37:04.000Z","msg":"藝人高鈞賢與天后容祖兒之前於大陸真人騷節目《全員加速中》合作後，二人又再於江蘇衛視的唱歌真人騷節目《看見你的聲音》中踫頭，今次高鈞賢更以歌手身份出現，更竟然請到內地視帝級的胡歌為他拍片「撐場」，難怪最後祖兒都選了高鈞賢與她合唱。<br />\n<br />\n孖祖兒合唱圓願<br />\n<br />\n其實能夠與祖兒合唱一向是高鈞賢的心願，今次居然於大陸真人騷節目一起唱歌，高鈞賢接受訪問時坦言：「其實約十年前我都同Joey合作過劇集《學警出更》，劇中我做佢男朋友，所以今次我一出現，Joey都即係話：『香港先生高鈞賢，佢做過我男朋友㗎！』」<br />\n<br />\n講到高鈞賢很大面子，能夠請得胡歌為他拍片撐場，對此他謂：「我去到大陸發展後，喺經理人介紹下認識到胡歌，佢個人好好，好多嘢都提點我，對新人好好。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160531/mobile/bkn-20160531182928286-0531_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160531%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20160531182928286-0531_00862_001.html&d=ghkbBml4OP7faEnvecWIPgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a8a9d150\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160531/mobile/bkn-20160531182928286-0531_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d7663a89300e91e7e26283c53bf4f66a967438c4","tid":710901,"uid":106027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T11:52:41.000Z","msg":"小泉響子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7673e449da7d205d64e74c83cb0e9667fd1a4f2","tid":710901,"uid":7958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82decc988d070ff4f760827a6c336b70c313b9a4","tid":710901,"uid":38102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:26:41.000Z","msg":"千秋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T12:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女當年係街啜高鈞賢比人影到 <br />\n真心好柒"},{"pid":"3b8e88fba82b349809792b2e1d1bc2acc7a29964","tid":710901,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T12:23:36.000Z","msg":"根本無線就係累死高鈞賢<br />\n搞到佢混混噩噩咁多年都唔知做乜"},{"pid":"d07291807e92317c86686c81434e8d76dd039b80","tid":710901,"uid":11523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b8e88fba82b349809792b2e1d1bc2acc7a29964","tid":710901,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0